DStv will host a new channel from 14 February, titled Moja Love. The channel, brought to viewers by Siyaya TV, will show content that “speaks to universal love in the African context”. “The 24-hour channel will be filled with fresh, new-to-air shows that are locally produced and primarily targeted at women,” states the channel’s press material. Moja Love will be available on DStv channel 157 for Premium, Compact Plus, Compact, and Family customers.